title: Cascading parameter values are not displayed properly in HTML viewer
description:
Description: Cascading parameter values are not displayed properly in the HTML viewer. 

Steps to reproduce:
1. Select the first parameter value in a cascading parameter group.

Expected behavior: 
- The second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group should be displayed.

Actual behavior: 
- The second parameter value is not displayed in the HTML viewer.
OB: The second parameter value in the cascading parameter group is not displayed in the HTML viewer.
EB: The second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group should be displayed, but it is not shown in the HTML viewer.
SR: Please fix the issue so that the second parameter value in the cascading parameter group is displayed correctly in the HTML viewer.
